<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 06 Mar 2026 12:31:15 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>针对老年人的团体与个人以悲伤为中心的认知行为疗法</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/group-vs-individual-grief-focused-cognitive-behavioral-therapy-for-older-adults</link><description>在一项针对老年人的随机临床试验中，针对 6 个月时的长期悲伤、创伤后应激障碍、抑郁和焦虑症状，以团体形式关注悲伤的认知行为疗法 (ProlongedGriefDisorder) 并不劣于个体疗法。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/group-vs-individual-grief-focused-cognitive-behavioral-therapy-for-older-adults2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Mar 2026 12:31:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/group-vs-individual-grief-focused-cognitive-behavioral-therapy-for-older-adults</guid></item><item><title>引力坍缩引发银河系磁力</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/gravitational-collapse-primes-galactic-magnetism</link><description>为膨胀的宇宙设计的坐标变换使人们对坍缩的原星系如何获得大磁场有了新的认识。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/gravitational-collapse-primes-galactic-magnetism2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Mar 2026 12:16:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/gravitational-collapse-primes-galactic-magnetism</guid></item><item><title>针对不断变化的天空启动警报系统</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/launching-an-alert-system-for-the-changing-sky</link><description>随着公共警报流的首次亮相，鲁宾天文台展示了近乎实时地报告来自超新星、变星、活跃星系核和小行星的瞬态信号的能力。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/launching-an-alert-system-for-the-changing-sky2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Mar 2026 12:01:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/launching-an-alert-system-for-the-changing-sky</guid></item><item><title>在电介质中模拟闪电</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/mimicking-lightning-in-a-dielectric</link><description>在介电材料中加速到相对论速度的电子可以产生 X 射线爆发，类似于雷暴中发现的现象。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/mimicking-lightning-in-a-dielectric2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Mar 2026 11:46:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/mimicking-lightning-in-a-dielectric</guid></item><item><title>人形机器人掌握跑酷并获得像人类一样的敏捷性</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/humanoid-robots-master-parkour-and-acquire-human-like-agility</link><description>人形机器人是具有类人身体结构的机器人系统，有潜力解决目前由人类完成的各种现实世界任务。近年来，许多机器人研究人员和计算机科学家一直在努力扩大这些机器人的能力并改善它们在周围环境中的移动方式。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/humanoid-robots-master-parkour-and-acquire-human-like-agility2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Mar 2026 11:31:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/humanoid-robots-master-parkour-and-acquire-human-like-agility</guid></item><item><title>使用可穿戴传感器聆听身体最安静但最动态的运动</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/listening-to-the-bodys-quietest-yet-most-dynamic-movements-with-a-wearable-sensor</link><description>人体不断产生丰富的振动频谱——通常我们都没有注意到。呼吸、说话和吞咽等日常无意识活动都会产生微妙但独特的机械信号。尽管这些微弱的振动携带着有关生理状态的宝贵信息，但长期以来很难使用传统的可穿戴设备准确捕获它们。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/listening-to-the-bodys-quietest-yet-most-dynamic-movements-with-a-wearable-sensor3.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Mar 2026 11:16:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/listening-to-the-bodys-quietest-yet-most-dynamic-movements-with-a-wearable-sensor</guid></item><item><title>热噪声可以训练计算机吗？新框架指向低功耗人工智能</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/can-thermal-noise-train-a-computer-a-new-framework-points-to-low-power-ai</link><description>如果阻碍经典计算机和量子计算机效率的热噪声可以用作电源呢？如果计算机可以利用噪声而不是抑制或克服噪声呢？这些是称为热力学计算的相对较新的计算分支的目标。分子铸造厂和国家能源研究科学计算中心 (NERSC) 的研究人员之间的合作使他们更接近现实，这两个中心都是美国能源部 (DOE) 用户设施，均位于劳伦斯伯克利国家实验室 (伯克利实验室)。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/can-thermal-noise-train-a-computer-a-new-framework-points-to-low-power-ai2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Mar 2026 11:01:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/can-thermal-noise-train-a-computer-a-new-framework-points-to-low-power-ai</guid></item><item><title>科学家创造出比真实钻石更硬的六角形钻石</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/scientists-create-a-hexagonal-diamond-that-could-be-even-harder-than-the-real-thing</link><description>错误地引用了一首著名歌曲：“钻石是行业最好的朋友。”立方金刚石是地球上最坚硬的矿物，用于从精密切割工具到高性能半导体以及昂贵的珠宝等各种领域。但有一种罕见且可能更坚硬的形式，称为六角金刚石 (HD)，长期以来，它一直是有关其实际存在的理论和争论的主题。但现在来自中国的研究人员声称已经在实验室中创造了这种难以捉摸的碳形式。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/scientists-create-a-hexagonal-diamond-that-could-be-even-harder-than-the-real-thing2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Mar 2026 10:46:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/scientists-create-a-hexagonal-diamond-that-could-be-even-harder-than-the-real-thing</guid></item><item><title>新的 LVK 目录增加了 128 个候选引力波，探测数量增加了一倍多</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/new-lvk-catalog-adds-128-gravitational-wave-candidates-more-than-doubling-detections</link><description>当宇宙中最稠密的物体碰撞并合并时，暴力会以引力波的形式引发涟漪，在空间和时间上产生回响，持续数亿甚至数十亿年。当它们穿过地球时，这种宇宙涟漪几乎难以辨别。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/new-lvk-catalog-adds-128-gravitational-wave-candidates-more-than-doubling-detections3.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Mar 2026 10:31:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/new-lvk-catalog-adds-128-gravitational-wave-candidates-more-than-doubling-detections</guid></item><item><title>中子揭示手性声子的磁性特征</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/neutrons-reveal-magnetic-signatures-of-chiral-phonons</link><description>中国物理学家发现了新的证据，证明手性声子和磁振子可以在磁性晶体内发生强烈相互作用。南京大学宋宝领导的团队利用中子光谱绘制了与亚铁磁材料中的手性声子相关的磁特征，揭示了晶格振动和磁激发之间以前难以捉摸的关系。报道于&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/neutrons-reveal-magnetic-signatures-of-chiral-phonons2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Mar 2026 10:16:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/neutrons-reveal-magnetic-signatures-of-chiral-phonons</guid></item></channel></rss>